{"tid":1508638,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔係突發] 麗晶最新情況","createTime":"2019-08-26T14:46:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T06:32:42.000Z","uid":254456,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"56b58fa65d437845d26b09f5fb39ce901e0928c0","tid":1508638,"uid":254456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:46:58.000Z","msg":"哈囉大家好！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又係我蛋撻哥哥<br />\n係聽我9up之前，麻煩睇一睇呢一個post : <br />\n<br />\n小弟麗晶居民，希望各位能聽小弟一席話<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1505484\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1505484</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">第一部分  最新狀況及問題</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n第一 兩個被捕街坊今日提堂，被控以「在公眾地方作出擾亂秩序的行為」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n立場報道 : <br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B6%89%E6%8B%8D%E6%89%93%E8%AD%A6%E8%BB%8A%E8%BA%AB-%E5%87%BA%E8%A8%80%E4%BE%AE%E8%BE%B1-%E9%BA%97%E6%99%B6%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E6%93%BE%E4%BA%82%E7%A7%A9%E5%BA%8F%E6%8F%90%E5%A0%82-%E5%87%86%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B10%E6%9C%88%E5%86%8D%E8%A8%8A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B6%2589%25E6%258B%258D%25E6%2589%2593%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25BB%258A%25E8%25BA%25AB-%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%25A8%2580%25E4%25BE%25AE%25E8%25BE%25B1-%25E9%25BA%2597%25E6%2599%25B6%25E5%25B1%2585%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%2593%25BE%25E4%25BA%2582%25E7%25A7%25A9%25E5%25BA%258F%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%25A0%2582-%25E5%2587%2586%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B10%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25A8%258A%2F&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsSuJrf%2BHou%2F%2F5XtIYOa%2FW4Y%3D&h=91c357c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B6%2589%25E6%258B%258D%25E6%2589%2593%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25BB%258A%25E8%25BA%25AB-%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%25A8%2580%25E4%25BE%25AE%25E8%25BE%25B1-%25E9%25BA%2597%25E6%2599%25B6%25E5%25B1%2585%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%2593%25BE%25E4%25BA%2582%25E7%25A7%25A9%25E5%25BA%258F%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%25A0%2582-%25E5%2587%2586%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B10%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25A8%258A%2F&h=9e7832e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B6%89%E6%8B%8D%E6%89%93%E8%AD%A6%E8%BB%8A%E8%BA%AB-%E5%87%BA%E8%A8%80%E4%BE%AE%E8%BE%B1-%E9%BA%97%E6%99%B6%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E6%93%BE%E4%BA%82%E7%A7%A9%E5%BA%8F%E6%8F%90%E5%A0%82-%E5%87%86%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B10%E6%9C%88%E5%86%8D%E8%A8%8A/</a><br />\n<br />\n第二 麗晶花園有嘅係根據公契所產生的<span style=\"color: red;\">「業主委員會」</span>，而唔係<span style=\"color: blue;\">「業主立案法團」</span> ， 所以係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冇法律效力</span></span>， 而多年從來無法籌集足夠的業權份數，推翻被建制派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />壟斷嘅業主委員會<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong> 第二部分 麗晶花園進入路線</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n琴日嘅Post講到聽日8月28日 ( 星期三 ) 晚上8時30分會有一個無法定效力嘅「資訊交流會」 畀各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />居民了解麗晶花園發生咩事<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n路線主要有兩條 : <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">路線 一</span><br />\n搭港鐵前往再轉乘51m小巴往麗晶<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QkKPr4N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQkKPr4N.jpg&h=82b921b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n ( 上圖為51m小巴麗晶總站 ) <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">路線 二</span><br />\n乘坐巴士至麗晶花園附近巴士站 ( 啟業、啟晴有巴士總站 ) <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/26/210401_23204b74b304dc80b7b052be1267e80e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F26%2F210401_23204b74b304dc80b7b052be1267e80e.jpg&h=13f61abb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n ( 上圖紅圈的地方係進入麗晶的地方及巴士站，藍圈則是羽毛球場位置 ) <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>第三部分 議員回應</strong></span></span><br />\n我喺7點嘅時候問譚文豪議員以及畢東尼議員能否出席「資訊交流會」，但兩位議員都冇回應<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日就去到咁多，有問題喺下面留言，我會盡快覆你<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44cc1368ffdd4c66af43bfe32657b1b11a94f85f","tid":1508638,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:47:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">求幫推</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">最新post 睇得清楚d + 加左明天有義士再審係頂！</span></span>(極正經)(請推至長期置頂)被捕義士進程，一個也不能少不只是口號！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1508237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1508237</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a77dc629cc18a00de4115cfad803377df1dc4088","tid":1508638,"uid":81408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:50:11.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0d75d7adfb72efbe362d5e165100bc262185410","tid":1508638,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:53:23.000Z","msg":"啲人去晒邊？點解管理處無人"},{"pid":"85b7e72936c54187e963f37bc19a734b573160e1","tid":1508638,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:54:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\