},{"pid":"5684aa45559ce3503fd296decde40f5dda5273d6","tid":1508638,"uid":53361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T15:13:22.000Z","msg":"so生死左未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28c96d44567ec9013865195688fcd04cc6d085c2","tid":1508638,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T15:14:23.000Z","msg":"死肥婆呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e58e05874e3dced00fa6bafa898aa835cf181042","tid":1508638,"uid":98795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T15:27:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5e5bd4ad7dea8498498a1533861dc8abefb824a","tid":1508638,"uid":254456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T15:29:43.000Z","msg":"幫手推下呀喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"746087dfbdc33f4e2383afa93b7c1e477d9c22de","tid":1508638,"uid":188058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T16:06:13.000Z","msg":"希望有住戶可以召集業主借個勢成立法團：<br />\n<br />\n1) 首先要有一位業主做召集人，而佢要有不少於5%業權份數的業主所委任(書面委任書)。業權份數大多係一個單位一份，實際要睇你份公契(DMC)點寫。如果真係一人一份業權份數，以麗晶5904個單位為例(ref:wiki)，有296個業主(296個簽名)委任召集人就可以召集會議。召集人有責任去土地注冊處查閱土地登記冊，確定各單位的業主姓名。查冊一般而言要收費，但係你可以向所屬地區的民政事務處申請一次性豁免業權查冊收費證明書，向土地註冊處免費索取業主紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n留意：Cap344入面講到明任何DMC上用作阻撓業主成立法團既條款會被Cap 344 override。所以公契係阻唔到成立法團既，最緊要係搵夠人。<br />\n<br />\n2) 召集會議。要留意會議通知的相關規定，好易被人從呢方面challenge個會議既正當性。業主會議通知在業主會議日期至少14天前送達每一名業主、公契經理人及公契授權人(如有的話)。送達方式包括當面遞交、郵寄往收件人最後為人所<br />\n知的地址，或放在業主單位／單位信箱內。以及貼在建築物的顯眼處，例如lift lobby。唔好預到剛剛14日，留起碼3,4日走盞。有授權書係可以代出席唔到既業主投票同計法定人數，無規定每人可以獲幾多份授權書。例如有100個業主授權我，而我本身又係業主，咁我出席就當係101個人出席，我個票係101個人既票。留意番授權書要在業主會議舉行前至少48小時前送交召集人，而召集人須向所有交授權書業主發出確認收據。<br />\n<br />\n3) 業主會議<br />\n呢個會既quorum係10%業主人數(同業權份數唔同既; 舉例︰1個單位的業權由多人共同擁有，會計算為1名業主，1名業主擁有多個單位，會計算為1名業主)。會議主持係召集人。業主每擁有一份業權份數，即有一票。投票過半數而又有不少於30%業權份數的業主支持就可以成立法團，之後再中選出委員會人數、委員等等。過半數係剩係計有投票既人。<br />\n<br />\nReference:<br />\n1) Cap 344<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap344!en-zh-Hant-HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap344%21en-zh-Hant-HK&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsSuJrf%2BHou%2F%2F5XtIYOa%2FW4Y%3D&h=b4916080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap344!en-zh-Hant-HK</a><br />\n2) <a href=\"https://www.buildingmgt.gov.hk/file_manager/tc/documents/foc/how_to_form_an_owners_corporation_tc.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.buildingmgt.gov.hk%2Ffile_manager%2Ftc%2Fdocuments%2Ffoc%2Fhow_to_form_an_owners_corporation_tc.pdf&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsSuJrf%2BHou%2F%2F5XtIYOa%2FW4Y%3D&h=d20b09d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.buildingmgt.gov.hk/file_manager/tc/documents/foc/how_to_form_an_owners_corporation_tc.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"e209a34308b6e524b96ecee883826d9613167e3b","tid":1508638,"uid":10484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T16:10:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ad8cd69884ce088bfaec2a84e74de04f6304940d","tid":1508638,"uid":29899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T16:10:43.000Z","msg":"28/8．31/8會出動既手足記住幫手宣傳埋1/9機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[9．1機場] 文宣集合 2.0<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1507880\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1507880</a><br />\n<br />\n現有文宣集合 (Google Drive)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1GCRs7ie1gwrmV6-388fnE5PnFq_jnbwe\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1GCRs7ie1gwrmV6-388fnE5PnFq_jnbwe&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsSuJrf%2BHou%2F%2F5XtIYOa%2FW4Y%3D&h=d4b5d22c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1GCRs7ie1gw